Class SocketMessage

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am22new.Network.Socket.SocketMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SocketMessage extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a message that can be sent or received via a socket connection. This class is used to encapsulate the necessary data for socket-based communication, including a command, an object, and an optional payload.
